## <a id="tut_datasetschema"></a>Data Set Schema

The sample Retail data set used in the tutorial exercises models an online retail store operation.  The store carries products.  Customers order the products.  The company delivers the products.

The Retail data set includes the following entities.  Orders and order line items are fact tables.  The other entities are represented in dimension tables.

